  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>potatoes </strong>(skins on) into small cubes, then add the <strong>potato cubes </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>dried</strong> <strong>sage</strong> (you’ll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 10 min</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1635849063658-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1635849063658-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1635849063658-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1635849063658-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1635849063658-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>finely</p><p>Add a large knob of <strong>butter </strong>to a bowl with 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the butter has melted, add the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>dried sage</strong></p><p>Add a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, give everything a good mix up and set aside to absorb – this is your <strong>stuffing mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1635849084184-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1635849084184-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
