          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-2-1635849084184-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim and halve the <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong></p><p>Roll the <strong>stuffing mix</strong> into 8 <span class=\"text-danger\">[16] </span>stuffing balls</p><p>Once the potatoes have had 10 min, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and add the <strong>stuffing balls</strong> and <strong>halved sprouts</strong> with a few knobs of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven and cook for 8 min further or until everything is starting to colour</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-2-1635849097667-x200.jpg",
