    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the nachos are cooking, grate the <strong>brie </strong>coarsely</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar</strong></p><p>Once the nachos are lightly browned, top them with the <strong>grated brie </strong>and <strong>cheddar</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
